              "fill": "#57534E",
              "textGrowth": "fixed-width",
              "width": "fill_container",
              "content": "The name is short, musical, easy for a child to say, and soft enough to feel like a toy instead of a utility app. The logo system stays chunky, friendly, and instantly readable at app-icon size.",
